  },
  "description": "Saturation des ressources sur l'ensemble des services du stack Swarm. Couvre le 4e signal doré. La latence, le taux d'erreur et le trafic nécessitent une instrumentation HTTP qui n'existe pas encore.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 100,
      "title": "Vue d'ensemble",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-main" },
      "description": "Nombre de conteneurs vus par cAdvisor sur les 2 dernières minutes, par service Swarm. Une chute signale un redémarrage ou un crash.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 1 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "showPercentChange": false,
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-main" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "count by (container_label_com_docker_swarm_service_name) (container_last_seen{container_label_com_docker_swarm_service_name=~\"mon-app_.*\",image!=\"\"})",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "{{container_label_com_docker_swarm_service_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Conteneurs actifs par service",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "id": 101,
      "title": "Saturation mémoire",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-main" },
      "description": "Mémoire utilisée rapportée à la limite définie dans stack.yml. C'est LE véritable indicateur de saturation : au-delà de 100 %, Docker tue le conteneur (OOM kill). Les services sans limite déclarée n'apparaissent pas.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "mappings": [],
          "max": 1,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.75 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.9 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percentunit"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 10, "x": 0, "y": 7 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "displayMode": "gradient",
        "maxVizHeight": 300,
        "minVizHeight": 16,
        "minVizWidth": 8,
        "namePlacement": "left",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "showUnfilled": true,
        "sizing": "auto",
        "valueMode": "color"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-main" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (container_label_com_docker_swarm_service_name) (container_memory_working_set_bytes{container_label_com_docker_swarm_service_name=~\"mon-app_.*\",image!=\"\"})\n/\nsum by (container_label_com_docker_swarm_service_name) (container_spec_memory_limit_bytes{container_label_com_docker_swarm_service_name=~\"mon-app_.*\",image!=\"\"} > 0)",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "{{container_label_com_docker_swarm_service_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Mémoire consommée / limite Swarm",
      "type": "bargauge"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-main" },
      "description": "Mémoire réellement occupée par service (working set : ce que le noyau ne peut pas récupérer sous pression).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "gradientMode": "opacity",
            "hideFrom": { "legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "normal" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "off" }
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }] },
          "unit": "bytes"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 14, "x": 10, "y": 7 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-main" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (container_label_com_docker_swarm_service_name) (container_memory_working_set_bytes{container_label_com_docker_swarm_service_name=~\"mon-app_.*\",image!=\"\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{container_label_com_docker_swarm_service_name}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Mémoire par service (empilée)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 15 },
      "id": 102,
      "title": "Saturation processeur",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-main" },
      "description": "Consommation processeur par service. 1 = un cœur entièrement occupé. Le VPS dispose de 4 cœurs : la somme empilée approchant 4 signifie que la machine sature.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "gradientMode": "opacity",
            "hideFrom": { "legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "normal" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "dashed" }
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "max": 4,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 3 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 3.6 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percentunit"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-main" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (container_label_com_docker_swarm_service_name) (rate(container_cpu_usage_seconds_total{container_label_com_docker_swarm_service_name=~\"mon-app_.*\",image!=\"\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{container_label_com_docker_swarm_service_name}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Processeur par service — cœurs consommés (VPS = 4 cœurs)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
